sequenceDiagram
    participant Git as Git Push
    participant Webhook as GitHub Webhook
    participant Server as gRPC Server
    participant GH as GitHub Contents API
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    Git->>Webhook: push event
    Webhook->>Server: POST /webhook
    Server->>Server: Parse changed cases/**/*.md paths
    Server->>GH: GET file content for each changed path
    GH-->>Server: File content
    Server->>PG: Upsert case from markdown front matter + body
    PG-->>Server: OK
